include va require orqali fayllani bir biriga ulasa boladi faqat  require bilan includeni bitta farqi. Includeda agarda ulagan faylimiz bomasa unaqa fayl ochmagan bose php kod
iwlavuradi.
Agar requireda ulagan faylimiz bomasa unaqa fayl ochmagan bose requireni tegidigi php kod iwlamidi farqi faqat wunda.
misol uchun:
<?php include 'inc/inc.php' ?>
<?php require 'inc/inc.php' ?>
Yana include_once va require_once yam bor bulada oddiy require bilan includedan farqi require bilan includeda holagancha bitta faylni ulasa boladi. 
A include_once va require_once birmatta iwlatsa boladi bowqa umuman iwlat bomidi faqat birmartta faylni ulasa boladi.
kodlari:
<?php include_once 'inc/inc.php' ?>
<?php require_once 'inc/inc.php' ?>
